</head>

<body>
        <%- include('partials/header') %>
        
    <div class="container">
        
        

        <main>
                
            
                <div class="main-banner-hero">
                                
                    <h1>Get Your Private Repair Quote</h1>

                    <div class="whatsapp-buttons">
                        <a href="https://wa.me/447448589086?text=Hi, I’d like to send images for a quote" class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">
                            <img src="/img/whatsapp-logo.png" alt="WhatsApp"> Send images
                        </a>
                    </div>
        
                
                    <h2>We provide transparent, 
                        fair repair cost estimates for <span>lease returns </span>and <span>private repairs</span> ,
                        connecting you with our trusted bodyshop network.</h2>
                
                </div>
    
            
        </main>

        <div id="sidebar">

            <div class="sidebar-why">

                <h1>HOW</h1>
                        <p>1. <span>Send your images</span> via WhatsApp. <br>
                            <br>2. <span>Receive your quote confirmation </span> on the email provided. <br>
                            <br>3. Make payment and <span>download your repair quote</span>.
                        </p>
                
                <h1>Why Choose Us</h1>
                    <p>We can provide written reliable private repair quotations from the comfort of your home. <br>
                    <br>You don't need to travel to different garages to obtain an written report.<br>
                    <br>Depending on your damage severity and your budget we can refer you in our trusted bodyshop network.
                        </p>
            
             

            </div>


            <div class="key-services">
                <h1>Key Services</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="sidebar-bodyshop-btn">             

                <a href="bodyshop">
                    <h1>Bodyshop <br> VDA Solution</h1>
                </a>
                </div>

             <div class="sidebar-quotations-btn">
                <a href="quotations">
                    <h1>Private <br>Quotations</h1>
                </a>
            </div>  
            
            <div class="sidebar-training-btn">
                <a href="training">
                    <h1>VDA Training</h1>
                </a>
            </div>  

        </div>

        <div id="content1">

            <div class="content1-about">
                <h1>About us</h1>
                <p>We are a team led by a highly qualified and experienced 
                    Senior ATA IMI Vehicle Damage Assessor with a Diploma 
                    in Mechanical Engineering and over 22 years in the motor industry.  
                    Our core strength lies in our ability to provide accurate and 
                    reliable vehicle damage assessments, driven by a combination 
                    of in-depth industry knowledge & technical proficiency.</p>
                    <p>Key skills and qualifications include:</p>
                        <ul class="skills-qualf-list">
                            <li>Senior ATA IMI Vehicle Damage Assessor accreditation(2017, 2021,2024)</li>
                            <li>Expertise in vehicle damage assessment and repair estimation</li>
                            <li>Proficiency in industry-standard software (e.g. GT Motive, Audatex)</li>
                            <li>Strong understanding of insurance claims processes</li>
                            <li>2:1 Hons in Mechanical Engineering</li>
                        </ul>

                    <p>We are committed to delivering high-quality services, 
                    adhering to industry best practices, and providing our clients 
                    with the information they need to make informed decisions.
                    
                    </p>
               
             </div>


        </div>       
                      
        <div id="content2">
            <h1>Fees</h1>

                    <div class="price-card">
                        <h3>Private Quotation for Repairs</h3>
                        <p>Independent repair cost estimate</p>
                        <span class="price">£25</span>
                    </div>
          
                    <div class="price-card">
                        <h3>Accident Damage Inspection</h3>
                        <p>Detailed report for insurance/legal use</p>
                        <span class="price">from £75 to £120</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="price-card">
                        <h3>Bodyshop Support Package</h3>
                        <p>On-site assessment & support</p>
                        <span class="price">From £100/day</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="price-card">
                        <h3>Training</h3>
                        <p>Vehicle Damage Assessing Booster</p>
                        <span class="price">From £150/hour</span>
                    </div>
            
       
        </div>


        <div id="content3">
                    
        
                <div class="container3" id="contact">
                    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                    <form action="/contact" method="POST">
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                          </div>
                      <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                  </div>
       
 

        </div>

   
   
        

        <footer>
                <%- include('partials/footer', { headerData: footerData }) %>
        </footer>

        
    </div>
    <script src="/js/mobile-nav.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
